    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/j0rgbv-09/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=612462497168884523&sectionId=612462497235993387)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggK36cgwamk_text","label":"ggK36cgwamk_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">The Italian Routine — A Guide To Your SerlinoLab Core Kit</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzxCZz2gq5_text","label":"ggzxCZz2gq5_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">Three products. Two minutes. Morning and night. This is the routine that works.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggAeeRopKnc_text","label":"ggAeeRopKnc_text","default":"<strong>Your Daily Routine</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg64GOh2eDx_text","label":"gg64GOh2eDx_text","default":"<strong>Morning</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_lm3QR6nr_text","label":"gg_lm3QR6nr_text","default":"Step 1 — Cleanse — SerlinoLab Face Wash"},{"type":"html","id":"ggTMUMNxJzW_text","label":"ggTMUMNxJzW_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\"><strong>Step 1 — Cleanse — SerlinoLab Face Wash</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggbpLREsor_text","label":"gggbpLREsor_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Start with a clean face. Remove the oil and residue from the night. Active ingredients absorb into clean skin — not on top of whatever built up overnight.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDthIAxs_6_text","label":"ggDthIAxs_6_text","default":"Step 2 — Eye Cream"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwR4bT3XZl_text","label":"ggwR4bT3XZl_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>Step 2 — Eye Cream</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLjq5WQEie_text","label":"ggLjq5WQEie_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Keep it in the fridge. The cold reduces puffiness faster and makes the product more effective.</span><br>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Squeeze a tiny amount — less than a pea. That's enough for both eyes. Dot along the orbital bone — the curved edge of the eye socket, not the eyelid. Use your ring finger only. Tap gently from the inner corner outward. Don't rub, don't drag.</span><br>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">More product does not mean better results. It sits on top of the skin and goes to waste.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzZVldmL9M_text","label":"ggzZVldmL9M_text","default":"<strong>Evening</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg8ospjT2J1_text","label":"gg8ospjT2J1_text","default":"Step 1 — Cleanse — SerlinoLab Face Wash"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRDCFhgrgU_text","label":"ggRDCFhgrgU_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>Step 1 — Cleanse — SerlinoLab Face Wash</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggegSxTS29j_text","label":"ggegSxTS29j_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Remove the day's buildup before anything else. Applying cream on top of dirt is like painting over rust — it won't work.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWoT1b_-Eh_text","label":"ggWoT1b_-Eh_text","default":"Step 2 — Eye Cream"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrBodN9Ldd_text","label":"ggrBodN9Ldd_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>Step 2 — Eye Cream</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggLdcL9wj3h_text","label":"ggLdcL9wj3h_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Same as the morning. Tiny amount, ring finger, tap along the orbital bone.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJ0n5V806-_text","label":"ggJ0n5V806-_text","default":"Step 3 — Night Cream"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEjZ5LQaBy_text","label":"ggEjZ5LQaBy_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:36px;\"><strong>Step 3 — Night Cream</strong></span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggnWQETxIVI_text","label":"ggnWQETxIVI_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Two presses — about the size of a small coin. The formula is concentrated. More does not mean faster results — it means you run out sooner. One bottle is designed to last 30 days at the correct dose.</span><br>&nbsp;<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Press gently into your face, neck, and jawline. Don't rub. Let the Retinyl Palmitate do the work overnight.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggn_A8Phlnt_text","label":"ggn_A8Phlnt_text","default":"<span style=\"background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">What To Expect</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0KM42e2GL_text","label":"gg0KM42e2GL_text","default":"Week 1–2"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXVzZvOIFl_text","label":"ggXVzZvOIFl_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Skin feels more hydrated. The tired, dull look starts to fade. Puffiness around the eyes begins to reduce.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggqiB4D3vmJ_text","label":"ggqiB4D3vmJ_text","default":"Week 3–4"},{"type":"html","id":"ggdQOXEFY85_text","label":"ggdQOXEFY85_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Skin texture smooths out. Fine lines at the corners of the eyes begin softening. Your face looks more rested, even on rough mornings.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggyGd4XtY1c_text","label":"ggyGd4XtY1c_text","default":"Week 6–8"},{"type":"html","id":"ggROrVBslzN_text","label":"ggROrVBslzN_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Under-eye hollows and dark circles visibly reduce. Deeper creases start softening. This is when people around you start noticing — without being able to say why.</span>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggKnh4dvsle_text","label":"ggKnh4dvsle_text","default":"Month 3+"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrGrL-0j7K_text","label":"ggrGrL-0j7K_text","default":"<span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">The longer you stay consistent, the more the results build. Don't stop after one jar.</span><br><span style=\"color:rgb(21,21,21);\">Consistency is everything. Don't run out mid-routine.</span>"}],
